'''谷语'''（[[外名与内名|内名]]：''{{IPA|ku55}}''）是一种在中国[[云南省|云南省]]东南的[[彝语支|彝语支]][[方言连续体|方言连续体]]。

==变体==
谷语有3种变体。<ref name="msealangs">{{cite web|url=https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/home|website=sites.google.com|title=MSEA Languages|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2020-10-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201009124628/https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/home|dead-url=no}}</ref>每个变体的使用者都认为他们是独立的民族。<ref name="Hsiu2013"/>中国政府将他们归为[[彝族|彝族]]。<ref>''丘北县志''（1999）</ref>

*谷语（内名：''ku55''）分布在[[云南省|云南省]][[丘北县|丘北县]][[舍得彝族乡|舍得彝族乡]]白泥塘<ref name="ynszxc">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=198759|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=丘北县舍得彝族乡矣白村民委白泥塘村|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2017-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202105550/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=198759|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他们在当地被称为[[僰人|僰人]]，至今仍有[[悬棺|悬棺]]的习俗。当地谷语使用者认为他们从四川[[宜宾市|宜宾市]]。<ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. ''[https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-bainitang Ku （Bainitang） audio word list] {{Wayback|url=https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-bainitang |date=20201009124619 }}''. Zenodo. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1122951}}</ref>

*谷语另一方言（内名：''ku55''）分布在[[云南省|云南省]][[丘北县|丘北县]][[舍得彝族乡|舍得彝族乡]]五家寨<ref name="ynszxc2">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=198738|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=丘北县舍得彝族乡舍得村民委五家寨村|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2017-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213013151/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=198738|dead-url=no}}</ref>，与白泥塘谷语不能互通。<ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. ''[https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-shidongmen Ku （Shidongmen） audio word list] {{Wayback|url=https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-shidongmen |date=20201009124619 }}''. Zenodo. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1123229}}</ref>

*[[云南省|云南省]][[广南县|广南县]][[珠琳镇|珠琳镇]]西基得村石洞门<ref name="ynszxc3">{{cite web|url=http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=86779|website=ynszxc.gov.cn|title=广南县珠琳镇西基德村委会石洞门|access-date=2017-12-30|archive-date=2017-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171227184107/http://www.ynszxc.gov.cn/villagePage/vIndex.aspx?departmentid=86779|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>Hsiu, Andrew. 2017. ''[https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-wujiazhai Ku （Wujiazhai） audio word list] {{Wayback|url=https://sites.google.com/site/msealangs/sino-tibetan/ku-wujiazhai |date=20201009124620 }}''. Zenodo. {{doi|10.5281/zenodo.1122945}}</ref>

